This repository also contains generated WebAssembly codec artifacts and build
scripts that use third-party C/C++ libraries. Those components remain under
their upstream licenses. See `THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md` for the codec dependency
license summary and source information.

Important notes
---------------

- `src/codecs/mp3/libmp3.wasm.mjs` is built with LAME and is subject to LAME's
  LGPL terms.
- `src/codecs/aac/libaac.wasm.mjs` is built with FFmpeg configured with
  `--disable-gpl` and is subject to FFmpeg's LGPL terms.
- `src/codecs/opus/libopus.wasm.mjs`, `src/codecs/flac/libflac.wasm.mjs`,
  `src/codecs/amr/libamrnb.wasm.mjs`, and `src/codecs/amr/libamrwb.wasm.mjs`
  include third-party codec libraries under their respective upstream licenses.
- The build scripts under `scripts/wasm/` document the exact upstream versions,
  download URLs, and source archive checksums used to build these artifacts.

No trademark, patent, or codec patent pool license is granted by this project
beyond the rights expressly granted by the applicable open source licenses.

